title: Magnus Walker & Her Lady Stunt
description: This week we are joined by enterneur and vintage Porsche icon, Magnus Walker. He send a trend for modifying  (and driving the crap out of) vintage 911s, and many have followed suit. Joining him is longtime TST friend and Hollywood stunt driver, Sera Trimble (@trims440), who tells us how she came to have the job we all envy.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
